source.name: Current Population Survey Work Schedules Supplement
source.description: A national survey conducted to obtain data on working hours and work shifts.  It also collects data on hours worked at home and equipment used.  The universe for this survey is each working individual in the household.  Proxy responses are accepted for this survey.
